						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up in the field called Tōpaṇṇanavara hola.</p>						

						<p>In late characters.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription of late characters mentions Basavaliṅgadēvara-maṭha and seems to refer to the construction of the tomb <hi rend="italic">(gaddige)</hi> of a teacher by Nāḍagaūḍa Liṅgahara Oḍeya.</p>						

